<div id="cause-card" class="card row">
  <div class="card-content white darken-1">
    <h3 class="col s12 center-align">Automatic Dispensing Cereal Bowl</h3>
    <div class="cause-info-container col s8">
      <div class="cause-img-container valign-wrapper center-align">
        <%= image_tag("http://2.bp.blogspot.com/_h4tLF5wFv0Q/RaGGhc9VF4I/AAAAAAAAAOw/tNXjEPlMx8I/s320/Picture+1.png", class: "valign") %>
      </div>
      <p>
        The path of the righteous man is beset on all sides by the iniquities of the selfish and the tyranny of evil men. Blessed is he who, in the name of charity and good will, shepherds the weak through the valley of darkness, for he is truly his brother's keeper and the finder of lost children. And I will strike down upon thee with great vengeance and furious anger those who would attempt to poison and destroy My brothers. And you will know My name is the Lord when I lay My vengeance upon thee.
      </p>
    </div> <!-- end of img and description column -->
    <div class="col s4 center">
      <div class="cause-stats-container center row">
        <div class="col s6">
          <p>Supporters:</p>
          <span>1</span>
          <p>Donations:</p>
          <span>1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col s6">
          <p>Amount Raised:</p>
          <span>$100</span>
          <p>Target Goal:</p>
          <span>$500</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="input-field">
        <!-- form for updating a cause will go here. placeholder input field -->
        <input id="donation_amount" type="text">
        <label for="donation_amount">Donation Amount ($)</label>
        <%= link_to "FUND THIS DREAM", "#", class: "btn light-green darken-4" %>
      </div> <!-- end of donation form -->
    </div> <!-- end of second cause card column -->
  </div> <!-- end of card content -->
</div> <!-- end of card row -->
